DTSTART:20150419T000000Z
DTEND:20150419T043000Z
DTSTAMP:20150330T164434Z
UID:bmla094q0k199vp9v923jj1c4k@google.com
CREATED:20150218T161253Z
DESCRIPTION:The Aromas-San Juan Bautista Community Schools Foundation is ho
 lding its 18th annual Fundraising dinner and auction on Saturday\, April 18
 th at the Aromas Grange Hall. The evening begins at 5:00 p.m. with a social
  hour. A delicious barbeque tri-tip and chicken dinner is followed by a liv
 ely auction featuring local wine\, art\, collectibles\, and student art. Th
 e Foundation supports arts in the schools\, provides assistance to educatio
 nal programs through mini-grants\, and provides annual scholarships and awa
 rds to district graduates.\nTickets cost $45 per person and can be purchase
 d through the school district office. Please order tickets by April 3rd. Co
 ntact a Foundation Board Member to buy tickets or make a donation.  \nMaril
 yn Breiling (831) 419-7230 (mcedar1@aol.com) or Heather Leeder at hleeder@s
 bcoe.org\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20150218T161253Z
LOCATION:Aromas Grange\, 400 Rose Avenue\, Aromas\, CA 95004\, United State
 s
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:SJB Comm Schools Foundation Dinner and Auction
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
